title: Anthony Atamanuik | Brian Knappenberger
description:
Anthony Atamanuik of The President Show joins Seth to discuss his Trump impression, and then speaks with Kevin Miller about why he runs his show like the White House.
Then, filmmaker Brian Knappenberger discusses press freedom in our current age. After his interview with Seth, he speaks further with Late Night producer Henry Melcher.
